## Troubleshooting
### Agent fails to start level
- Check ADK_API_KEY in `.env`
- Verify game API is accessible
- Check network connectivity
### Memory errors
- Ensure `memory/data/` directory is writable
- Check disk space
- Verify JSON file integrity
### Poor performance
- Increase `max_moves_per_level` in coordinator
- Adjust learning rate and rewards
- Review and reset corrupted knowledge
### Reset everything
```bash
# In interactive mode
>>> reset
Or manually delete `memory/data/*.json`
